<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="scold-v">scold <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /skəʊld/    美 /skoʊld/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>责骂；斥责：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Be grateful to those who have scolded you, as they reminded you of your faults. 
感谢那些斥责你的人，因为他们提醒了你的缺点。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>scold sb for (doing) sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Her father scolded her for upsetting her mother. 
她因惹母亲生气而被父亲斥责。</p></div></div>